<LegalLayout
  title="Pricing"
  description="PatientBillGuide is free to use. Supported by advertising, with no paid upsells."
  crumbs={[{ label: 'Pricing' }]}
>
  <h2>Free forever for users</h2>
  <p>
    All PatientBillGuide tools are <strong>free</strong>. We do not charge for price checks,
    bill review, or letter templates. We do not sell your bill data.
  </p>

  <h2>How we sustain the site</h2>
  <p>
    We plan to support the site through <strong>Google AdSense</strong> and, later, carefully
    disclosed affiliate links in educational content (for example, bill advocacy resources).
    We will never gate core tools behind a paywall.
  </p>

  <h2>No upsell pressure</h2>
  <p>
    We are an independent guide — not a hospital, insurer, or collections agency. Tools are
    designed to inform, not to scare you into paid services.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
